{"id": 243302376, "title": "Argentina&#8217;s problems grow.. Scaloni suspended after Messi&#8217;s absence", "text": "The South American Football Confederation announced in a statement that Argentina coach Lionel Scaloni and Chile coach Ricardo Gareca have been suspended for one match each after their teams entered the pitch late during the 2024 Copa America. The 2022 world champions\u2019 problems deepened after star player Lionel Messi was ruled out with injury and defending champions Argentina were late to take to the pitch in the second half of their opening match against Canada last week, with coach Jesse Marsch saying Scaloni\u2019s team should be fined. Gareca was late in bringing on a player at the start of the second half against Argentina last Tuesday. The South American Football Confederation said: \u201cThe coaches have been suspended for one match each after their teams failed to comply with Articles 104 and 145 of the tournament regulations, which relate to being late to the pitch at the start of the match, or when play resumes.\u201d The two coaches will not be able to sit on the bench when the two teams complete the group stage on Saturday. In addition, the Argentine and Chilean football associations were fined $15,000 each. Argentina top Group A with six points and have already qualified for the last eight, where they will face Peru on Saturday, while Chile, who have just one point, will play group runners-up Canada.", "summary": "<p>The South American Football Confederation announced in a statement that Argentina coach Lionel Scaloni and Chile coach Ricardo Gareca have been suspended for one match each after their teams entered the pitch late during the 2024 Copa America. The 2022 world champions&#8217; problems deepened after star player Lionel Messi was ruled out with injury and [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://thenewsglory.com/argentinas-problems-grow-scaloni-suspended-after-messis-absence/\">Argentina&#8217;s problems grow.. Scaloni suspended after Messi&#8217;s absence</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://thenewsglory.com\">The News Glory</a>.</p>", "url": "https://thenewsglory.com/argentinas-problems-grow-scaloni-suspended-after-messis-absence/", "image": "https://www.emaratalyoum.com/polopoly_fs/1.1864191.1719633845!/image/image.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-29 04:04:26", "author": "The News Glory", "authors": ["The News Glory"], "language": "en", "catgory": "politics", "source_country": "in", "sentiment": 0.198}